<!DOCTYPE html>

<!-- Hi, there! Earlier you saw this page in action. Now you can see what it looks behind the scenes! -->

<!-- First, we have the head where is stored the info that the computer needs in order to display the page as you wish. That is the head. -->

<head>
	<link href="styles/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

